            "body": "## Proposal\r\n\r\n### Please re-state the problem that we are trying to solve in this issue.\r\n\r\nmWeb/Safari - Chat - After removing an emoji and adding a new, the focus shifts the top of the page\r\n\r\n### What is the root cause of that problem?\r\n\r\nWhen finishing the edition, the method `deleteDraft` is called to act to draft the comment being edited. In this method, there is a condition to check if the user is editing the last message, if so, an event listener will be added to monitoring the event `keyboardDidHide` in the `Keyboard` object. But adding an event listener to the `Keyboard` object will only work on native devices, in this case, we are using a Mobile Browser. \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/Expensify/App/blob/72e73ae6d922b915198e0a5bcff9d71de5a1001b/src/pages/home/report/ReportActionItemMessageEdit.js#L297-L302\r\n\r\n### What changes do you think we should make in order to solve the problem?\r\n\r\nWe should improve the method `deleteDraft` in the `ReportActionItemMessageEdit` component to execute the scroll when the user finishs the edition and they are using a Mobile Browser\r\n\r\nFor example,\r\n\r\n```js\r\n/**\r\n * Delete the draft of the comment being edited. This will take the comment out of \"edit mode\" with the old content.\r\n */\r\nconst deleteDraft = useCallback(() => {\r\n    InputFocus.callback(() => setIsFocused(false));\r\n    InputFocus.inputFocusChange(false);\r\n    debouncedSaveDraft.cancel();\r\n    Report.saveReportActionDraft(props.reportID, props.action, '');\r\n\r\n    if (isActive()) {\r\n        ReportActionComposeFocusManager.clear();\r\n        ReportActionComposeFocusManager.focus();\r\n    }\r\n    // Scroll to the last comment after editing to make sure the whole comment is clearly visible in the report.\r\n    if (props.index === 0) {\r\n        if(Browser.isMobile()) { // <- Here is the new condition\r\n            setTimeout(() => reportScrollManager.scrollToIndex(props.index, false), CONST.ANIMATED_TRANSITION);\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        const keyboardDidHideListener = Keyboard.addListener('keyboardDidHide', () => {\r\n            reportScrollManager.scrollToIndex(props.index, false);\r\n            keyboardDidHideListener.remove();\r\n        });\r\n    }\r\n}, [props.action, debouncedSaveDraft, props.index, props.reportID, reportScrollManager, isActive]);\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Note**: There is a delay `setTimeout` just to wait for the Report Screen to be updated.\r\n\r\n### What alternative solutions did you explore? (Optional)\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n\r\n**POC**\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/Expensify/App/assets/698363/2e9771a7-617c-4b3f-96ae-41ee783ddeba\r\n\r\n\r\n",
