            "body": "Hi @hoangzinh thank you for reviewing my proposal.\r\n\r\nAbout your question, In my analysis, I understood the problem is only related when we edit the message and add a new emoji because when the emoji modal is shown the component's height changes and the position changes in the scroll view.\r\n\r\nIf you edit the emoji only removing information and saving you'll see that the strange behavior won't occur but if you edit the emoji removing and adding another one, the strange behavior will occur. In the video below you can see when the emoji modal opens in the messages in the background change their position.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/Expensify/App/assets/698363/1383f902-9626-4e48-8635-522fe470ef8a\r\n\r\n",
